{"prompt": "Generate a clean website for a corporate event planning firm. The brand color should be a deep plum.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elysian Events - Corporate Event Planning</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #6A0DAD; /* Deep Plum */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #6A0DAD 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 36px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header nav {\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        header nav ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        header nav ul li a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        header nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #e0c4ff; /* Lighter shade of plum */\n        }\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\"><path fill=\"%236A0DAD\" fill-opacity=\"1\" d=\"M0,192L48,213.3C96,235,192,277,288,293.3C384,309,480,315,576,293.3C672,272,768,224,864,213.3C960,203,1056,235,1152,234.7C1248,235,1344,203,1392,186.7L1440,171L1440,0L1392,0C1344,0,1248,0,1152,0C1056,0,960,0,864,0C768,0,672,0,576,0C480,0,384,0,288,0C192,0,96,0,48,0L0,0Z\"></path></svg>') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(106, 13, 173, 0.6); /* Deep Plum with transparency */\n        }\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #services h2, #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #6A0DAD;\n        }\n        .service-item, .about-content {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-left: 5px solid #6A0DAD;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #6A0DAD;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-left: 5px solid #6A0DAD;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #6A0DAD;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #8e44ad; /* Lighter shade of plum */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 30px;\n            }\n            header nav ul {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                gap: 10px;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 36px;\n            }\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 20px;\n            }\n            .service-item, .about-content, .contact-form {\n                border-left: none;\n                border-top: 5px solid #6A0DAD;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Elysian Events</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Transforming Visions into Unforgettable Experiences</h2>\n            <p>Your premier partner for exceptional corporate events.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Event Strategy & Design</h3>\n                <p>We conceptualize and design events that align with your brand objectives, creating immersive and engaging experiences for your guests.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Logistics & Management</h3>\n                <p>From venue selection and vendor management to on-site coordination, we handle every detail with precision and professionalism.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Creative Execution</h3>\n                <p>Bringing your event to life with bespoke decor, innovative entertainment, and seamless audiovisual integration.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Elysian Events</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>Elysian Events is dedicated to crafting extraordinary corporate events that leave a lasting impression. With a passion for detail and a commitment to excellence, our team of seasoned professionals works collaboratively with you to understand your vision and deliver flawlessly executed events that exceed expectations. Whether it's a product launch, conference, gala dinner, or team-building retreat, we ensure every element contributes to a successful and memorable occasion.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Let's discuss your next event!</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elysian Events. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}